  <para style="h">U-Amosi</para>
  <para style="toc1">U-Amosi</para>
  <para style="toc2">U-Amosi</para>
  <para style="toc3">Ams</para>
  <para style="mt1">U-Amosi</para>
  <para style="imt">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="imt1">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="im">Umbuso wako-Israyeli owawungenyakatho wadlondlobala ngeminyaka yakuqala yengxenye yesentshuri yesificaminwembili uKhristu engakazalwa (2 Amakhosi 14.23-25) ngomnyaka wamatshumi amane lanye wokubusa kukaJerobhowamu wesibili owayelamandla amakhulu. Babenamile ngokunqoba kwesizwe sabo, ukukhonza kwabo, ilifa labo njalo abantu baze babalesitsho sokuthi “UNkulunkulu ulathi!” Babekhangelele <char style="qt">usuku lukaThixo,</char> lapho uNkulunkulu ayezachitha khona izitha zabo zonke abesefaka u-Israyeli ukuthi abe ngumbusi ongelakuphikiswa.</para>
  <para style="ip">Esimeni esinjalo sokwenama kokuzibusa kufika u-Amosi, umelusi wezimvu evelela embusweni osezansi koJuda. Nxa ethempelini elikhulu lesikhosini eBhetheli amemezele ukuba uNkulunkulu useqoqa isizwe esizanqoba u-Israyeli. Wagcizelela ukuba <char style="qt">Usuku lukaThixo luzakuba yibumnyama hatshi ukukhanya.</char> UNkulunkulu kathokozi ngenotho ka-Israyeli, amandla ebutho lakhe lokulandela inkanuko zabo ekuphileni kwabo. Udinga ukulunga ngesikhathi izinothi labalamandla bencindezela abayanga. UNkulunkulu ubiza u-Israyeli ukuba aphenduke okuyiyona ndlela eyodwa yokuvikela ukubhidlizwa.</para>
  <para style="ip">Umbiko lo udala ukuvungama lokungahlaliseki. U-Amaziya, umphristi omkhulu weBhetheli ucala u-Amosi ngecala lokufuna ukugenqula umbuso. U-Amosi uyaxotshwa elizweni, kodwa iziphrofethi zakhe ziyalotshwa, okwaba liqoqo lakuqala elalotshwa ngumphrofethi ongumHebheru. Ugwalo lwakhe luqukethe iziphrofethi ezitshiyeneyo ezingaba ngamatshumi amathathu alesithupha kanye lodaba lokuxotshwa kwakhe. Phose ugwalo lonke kalubuthaniswanga ngokuqinileyo kodwa luletha umbiko munye omqoka njalo oqukethe nkulumo yinye ethi: <char style="qt">Ukwahlulela kuhle akugeleze njengomfula, lokulunga njengesiziba esingacitshiyo!</char></para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="AMO 1"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="AMO 1:1"/>La ngamazwi ka-Amosi, omunye wabelusi baseThekhowa, lokho akubonayo mayelana lo-Israyeli eminyakeni emibili ngaphambi kokuzamazama komhlaba, ngezinsuku u-Uziya eyinkosi yakoJuda loJerobhowamu indodana kaJowashi eyinkosi yako-Israyeli.<verse eid="AMO 1:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="AMO 1:2"/>Wathi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 1:2">“<char style="nd">UThixo</char> uyavungama eseZiyoni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:2">idume iJerusalema;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 1:2">amadlelo abelusi ayoma</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:2">lengqongo yeKhameli iyabuna.”<verse eid="AMO 1:2"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukwahlulelwa Kwabakhelene Lo-Israyeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="AMO 1:3"/>Nanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 1:3">“Ngenxa yezono ezintathu zeDamaseko,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:3">loba ngenxa yezine,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:3">kangiyikulunqanda ulaka lwami.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 1:3">Ngenxa yokuthi yatshaya iGiliyadi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:3">ngemibhulo elamazinyo ensimbi,<verse eid="AMO 1:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="AMO 1:4"/>ngizathumela umlilo endlini kaHazayeli</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:4">ozalobisa izinqaba zikaBheni-Hadadi.<verse eid="AMO 1:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="AMO 1:5"/>Ngizabhidliza isango laseDamaseko;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:5">ngizachitha inkosi ephakathi kweSigodi sase-Aveni</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 1:5">lalowo ophethe intonga yobukhosi eBhethi Edeni.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:5">Abantu base-Aramu bazathunjwa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:5">basiwe eKhiri,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:5">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.<verse eid="AMO 1:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="AMO 1:6"/>Nanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 1:6">“Ngenxa yezono ezintathu zeGaza</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:6">loba ngenxa yezine,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:6">kangiyikulunqanda ulaka lwami</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 1:6">ngenxa yokuthi yathumba abantu bezigaba zonke</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:6">yabathengisa e-Edomi,<verse eid="AMO 1:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="AMO 1:7"/>ngizathumela umlilo emidulini yaseGaza</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:7">ozalobisa izinqaba zayo.<verse eid="AMO 1:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="AMO 1:8"/>Ngizayichitha inkosi yase-Ashidodi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:8">kanye lalowo ophatha intonga yobukhosi e-Ashikheloni.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 1:8">Ngizaphendulela isandla sami ekuhlaseleni i-Ekroni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:8">kuze kufe umFilistiya wokucina,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:8">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> Wobukhosi.<verse eid="AMO 1:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="AMO 1:9"/>Nanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 1:9">“Ngenxa yezono ezintathu zaseThire</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:9">loba ngenxa yezine, kangiyikulunqanda ulaka lwami.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 1:9">Ngenxa yokuthi yabathengisela e-Edomi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:9">bonke abantu bezigaba zonke ezathunjwayo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:9">inganaki isivumelwano sobuzalwane,<verse eid="AMO 1:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="AMO 1:10"/>ngizathumela umlilo emidulini yaseThire</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:10">ozalobisa izinqaba zayo.”<verse eid="AMO 1:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="AMO 1:11"/>Nanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 1:11">“Ngenxa yezono ezintathu zase-Edomi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:11">loba ngenxa yezine, kangiyikulunqanda ulaka lwami.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 1:11">Ngenxa yokuthi waxotshana lomfowabo ngenkemba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:11">enqabela isihawu sonke,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 1:11">ngoba ulaka lwakhe lwavutha kokuphela</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:11">lentukuthelo yakhe yabhebha ingelakuthitshwa,<verse eid="AMO 1:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="AMO 1:12"/>ngizathumela umlilo eThemani</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:12">ozalobisa izinqaba zaseBhozira.”<verse eid="AMO 1:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="AMO 1:13"/>Nanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 1:13">“Ngenxa yezono ezintathu zase-Amoni, loba langenxa yezine,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:13">kangiyikulunqanda ulaka lwami.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 1:13">Ngenxa yokuthi waqhaqha abesifazane abazithweleyo baseGiliyadi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:13">ukuze aqhelise ilizwe lakhe,<verse eid="AMO 1:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="AMO 1:14"/>ngizathungela imiduli yaseRaba ngomlilo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:14">ozalobisa izinqaba zayo</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 1:14">kumenyezelwa izitsho zempi ngosuku lokulwa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:14">kulomoya olamandla ngosuku lwesiphepho.<verse eid="AMO 1:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="AMO 1:15"/>Inkosi yalo izathunjwa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:15">yona kanye lezikhulu zayo,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 1:15">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.<verse eid="AMO 1:15"/></para>
  <chapter eid="AMO 1"/>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" sid="AMO 2"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="AMO 2:1"/>Nanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 2:1">“Ngenxa yezono ezintathu zaseMowabi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:1">loba ngenxa yezine, kangiyikulunqanda ulaka lwami,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 2:1">ngoba utshise amathambo enkosi yase-Edomi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:1">aze afana lekalaga,<verse eid="AMO 2:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="AMO 2:2"/>ngizathumela umlilo kuMowabi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:2">ozalobisa izinqaba zaseKheriyothi.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 2:2">UMowabi uzachitheka kulokuxokozela okukhulu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:2">lokumenyezelwa kwezitsho zempi lokukhala kwecilongo.<verse eid="AMO 2:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="AMO 2:3"/>Ngizaqothula ababusi bakhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:3">ngibulale zonke izikhulu zakhe kanye laye,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:3">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.<verse eid="AMO 2:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="AMO 2:4"/>Nanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 2:4">“Ngenxa yezono ezintathu zikaJuda</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:4">loba ngenxa yezine, kangiyikulunqanda ulaka lwami,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 2:4">ngoba bawalile umthetho <char style="nd">kaThixo</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:4">kabaze bagcina lezimiso zakhe,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 2:4">ngoba badukiswe ngonkulunkulu bamanga,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:4">onkulunkulu abalandelwa ngokhokho babo.<verse eid="AMO 2:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="AMO 2:5"/>Ngizathumela umlilo koJuda</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:5">ozalobisa izinqaba zaseJerusalema.”<verse eid="AMO 2:5"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukwahlulelwa Kuka-Israyeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="AMO 2:6"/>Nanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 2:6">“Ngenxa yezono ezintathu zika-Israyeli</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:6">loba ngenxa yezine, kangiyikulunqanda ulaka lwami</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 2:6">ngoba bathengisa abalungileyo ngesiliva,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:6">labaswelayo ngamanyathelo.<verse eid="AMO 2:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="AMO 2:7"/>Banyathela phezu kwamakhanda abayanga</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:7">njengaphezu kothuli lomhlabathi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:7">banqabele imfanelo yabancindezelweyo.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 2:7">Uyise lendodana bembatha lentombi yinye</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:7">kanjalo bangcolise ibizo lami elingcwele.<verse eid="AMO 2:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="AMO 2:8"/>Bacambalala phansi emaceleni ama-alithare wonke,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:8">phezu kwezembatho ezithethwe ziyizibambiso.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 2:8">Endlini kankulunkulu wabo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:8">banatha iwayini elithethwe njengenhlawulo.<verse eid="AMO 2:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="AMO 2:9"/>Ngachitha umʼAmori phambi kwabo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:9">lanxa wayemude njengemisedari</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:9">njalo eqine njengomʼokhi.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 2:9">Ngachitha izithelo zakhe phezulu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:9">kanye lempande zakhe ngaphansi.<verse eid="AMO 2:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="AMO 2:10"/>Ngalikhupha eGibhithe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:10">ngalikhokhela iminyaka engamatshumi amane enkangala</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:10">ukuba ngilinike ilizwe lama-Amori.<verse eid="AMO 2:10"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="AMO 2:11"/>Ngakhupha labaphrofethi bephuma phakathi kwamadodana enu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:11">kanye lamaNaziri ephuma phakathi kwezinsizwa zenu.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 2:11">Lokhu akuqotho na, bantu bako-Israyeli?”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:11">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.<verse eid="AMO 2:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="AMO 2:12"/>“Kodwa lanathisa amaNaziri iwayini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:12">lalaya abaphrofethi ukuba bangaphrofethi.<verse eid="AMO 2:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="AMO 2:13"/>Khathesi-ke mina ngizalichoboza</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:13">njengokuchoboza kwenqola ithwele amabele.<verse eid="AMO 2:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="AMO 2:14"/>Olejubane kayikubaleka,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:14">oqinileyo uzawaswela amandla akhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:14">lebutho kaliyikusindisa impilo yalo.<verse eid="AMO 2:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="AMO 2:15"/>Umtshoki akayikugxila,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:15">ibutho elilejubane kaliyikuphunyuka</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:15">lomgadi webhiza kayikusindisa impilo yakhe.<verse eid="AMO 2:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="AMO 2:16"/>Lebutho elilesibindi kakhulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:16">ngalolosuku lizabaleka linqunu,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 2:16">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.<verse eid="AMO 2:16"/></para>
  <chapter eid="AMO 2"/>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" sid="AMO 3"/>
  <para style="s1">Ofakazi Bokumelana Lo-Israyeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="AMO 3:1"/>Zwanini ilizwi elikhulunywe <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> ngani lina bantu bako-Israyeli Lomndeni wonke engawukhupha eGibhithe:<verse eid="AMO 3:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="AMO 3:2"/>“Yini kuphela engalikhethayo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:2">kuyo yonke imideni yasemhlabeni;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 3:2">ngakho ngizalijezisela</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:2">zonke izono zenu.”<verse eid="AMO 3:2"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="AMO 3:3"/>Ababili bayahamba bendawonye</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:3">ngaphandle kokuba bevumelene ukwenzanjalo na?<verse eid="AMO 3:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="AMO 3:4"/>Isilwane siyabhonga ehlathini</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:4">kungelalutho esingalubamba na?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 3:4">Siyabhonga esikhundleni saso</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:4">singabambanga lutho na?<verse eid="AMO 3:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="AMO 3:5"/>Inyoni iyabanjwa emhlabathini</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:5">okungelamjibila othiywe khona na?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 3:5">Umjibila uyathanca usuke emhlabathini</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:5">kungelalutho olubambayo na?<verse eid="AMO 3:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="AMO 3:6"/>Lapho icilongo likhala edolobheni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:6">abantu kabethuki na?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 3:6">Lapho incithakalo isehlela idolobho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:6">kayenziwanga <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> na?<verse eid="AMO 3:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="AMO 3:7"/>Impela <char style="nd">uThixo</char> Wobukhosi kenzi lutho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:7">engavezanga icebo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:7">lakhe ezincekwini zakhe abaphrofethi.<verse eid="AMO 3:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="AMO 3:8"/>Isilwane sibhongile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:8">ngubani ongayikwesaba na?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 3:8">
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> Wobukhosi usekhulumile</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:8">ngubani ongayekela ukuphrofitha na?<verse eid="AMO 3:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="AMO 3:9"/>Memezelani ezinqabeni zase-Ashidodi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:9">lasezinqabeni zaseGibhithe lithi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 3:9">“Buthanani phezu kwezintaba zaseSamariya;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:9">libone isiyaluyalu esikhulu phakathi kwayo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:9">lokuncindezela phakathi kwabantu bayo.”<verse eid="AMO 3:9"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="AMO 3:10"/>“Kabakwazi ukwenza okulungileyo,” kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:10">“bona ababuthelela impango</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:10">baphange lasezinqabeni zabo.”<verse eid="AMO 3:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="AMO 3:11"/>Ngakho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> Wobukhosi uthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 3:11">“Isitha sizachitha ilizwe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:11">sizadiliza izinqaba zenu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:11">siphange izinqaba zenu.”<verse eid="AMO 3:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="AMO 3:12"/>Nanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 3:12">“Njengomelusi ehlenga emlonyeni wesilwane</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:12">amathambo amabili kuphela omlenze loba isiqa sendlebe,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 3:12">bazahlengwa kanjalo abako-Israyeli abahlala eSamariya</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:12">bethithibele ekucineni kwemibheda yabo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:12">kanye laseDamaseko phezu kwemibheda yabo yokuphumulela.”<verse eid="AMO 3:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="AMO 3:13"/>“Zwanini lokhu lifakaze ngendlu kaJakhobe,” kutsho iNkosi, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu uSomandla.<verse eid="AMO 3:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="AMO 3:14"/>“Ngosuku engizajezisela u-Israyeli izono zakhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:14">ngizabhidliza ama-alithare aseBhetheli;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 3:14">impondo ze-alithare zizaqunywa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:14">ziwele emhlabathini.<verse eid="AMO 3:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="AMO 3:15"/>Ngizadiliza indlu yebusika kanye</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:15">lendlu yehlobo,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 3:15">izindlu eziceciswe ngempondo zendlovu zizadilizwa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:15">lezindlu ezinkulu zizabhidlizwa,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 3:15">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.<verse eid="AMO 3:15"/></para>
  <chapter eid="AMO 3"/>
  <chapter number="4" style="c" sid="AMO 4"/>
  <para style="s1">U-Israyeli Kakabuyeli KuNkulunkulu</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="AMO 4:1"/>Zwanini ilizwi leli lina mankomokazi aseBhashani phezu kweNtaba iSamariya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:1">lina besifazane elincindezela abayanga lichoboze abaswelayo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:1">beselisithi kubomkenu, “Siletheleni okunathwayo!”<verse eid="AMO 4:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="AMO 4:2"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> Wobukhosi usefunge ngobungcwele bakhe wathi:</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:2">“Isikhathi sizafika impela</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 4:2">lapho elizathathwa khona ngewuka,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:2">owokucina wenu ngewuka yenhlanzi.<verse eid="AMO 4:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="AMO 4:3"/>Lizaphuma ngamunye</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:3">ngezikhala emdulini liqonde nta phandle,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 4:3">njalo lizalahlelwa ngaphandle ngokuya eHamoni,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:3">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.<verse eid="AMO 4:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="AMO 4:4"/>“Hambani eBhetheli liyekwenza isono;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:4">hambani eGiligali liyekwenza isono ngokudlulayo.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 4:4">Lethani imihlatshelo yenu nsuku zonke ekuseni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:4">lokwetshumi kwenu minyaka yonke emithathu.<verse eid="AMO 4:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="AMO 4:5"/>Tshisani isinkwa esilemvubelo njengomnikelo wokubonga</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:5">lintele ngeminikelo yenu yokuzithandela</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 4:5">lizikhukhumeze ngayo, lina bako-Israyeli,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:5">ngoba lokhu yikho elithanda ukukwenza,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:5">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> Wobukhosi.<verse eid="AMO 4:5"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="AMO 4:6"/>“Ngalilethela indlala emadolobheni wonke</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:6">lokusweleka kokudla emadolobheni wonke,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 4:6">kodwa kalibuyelanga kimi,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:6">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.<verse eid="AMO 4:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="AMO 4:7"/>“Ngagodla izulu futhi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:7">kusasele inyanga ezintathu ukuba kuvunwe.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 4:7">Izulu ngalinisa kwelinye idolobho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:7">kodwa ngaligodla kwelinye.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 4:7">Enye insimu yaba lezulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:7">enye kayaze yaba lalo njalo yoma qha.<verse eid="AMO 4:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="AMO 4:8"/>Abantu babhadazela besuka kwelinye idolobho besiya kwelinye befuna amanzi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:8">kodwa kabawatholanga anele ukuba bakholwe,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 4:8">ikanti kalibuyelanga kimi,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:8">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.<verse eid="AMO 4:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="AMO 4:9"/>“Ezikhathini ezinengi ngahlasela izivande zenu lezivini zenu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:9">ngizihlasela ngesona langengumane.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 4:9">Izintethe zadla imikhiwa yenu lezihlahla zenu zama-oliva,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:9">kodwa kalibuyelanga kimi,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:9">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.<verse eid="AMO 4:9"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="AMO 4:10"/>“Ngathumela izifo phakathi kwenu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:10">njengengakwenza kweleGibhithe.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 4:10">Ngabulala izinsizwa zenu ngenkemba</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:10">ndawonye lamabhiza enu athunjwayo.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 4:10">Ngavimbanisa amakhala enu ngomnuko wezihonqo zenu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:10">kodwa kalibuyelanga kimi,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:10">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.<verse eid="AMO 4:10"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="AMO 4:11"/>“Ngachitha abanye benu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:11">njengalokhu ngachitha iSodoma leGomora.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 4:11">Lalinjengesikhuni esitshayo esihluthunwe emlilweni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:11">kodwa kalibuyelanga kimi,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:11">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.<verse eid="AMO 4:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="AMO 4:12"/>“Ngakho-ke engizakwenza kuwe Israyeli yilokhu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:12">njalo njengoba lokhu ngizakwenza kuwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:12">zilungisele ukuhlangana loNkulunkulu wakho, wena Israyeli.”<verse eid="AMO 4:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="AMO 4:13"/>Yena obumba izintaba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:13">udala umoya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:13">aveze lemicabango yakhe ebantwini,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 4:13">yena oguqula ukusa kube ngumnyama,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:13">anyathele lezindawo eziphakemeyo zomhlaba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 4:13">
    <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu uSomandla yilo ibizo lakhe.<verse eid="AMO 4:13"/></para>
  <chapter eid="AMO 4"/>
  <chapter number="5" style="c" sid="AMO 5"/>
  <para style="s1">Isililo Lesimemezelo Sokuphenduka</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="AMO 5:1"/>Zwana ilizwi leli, wena ndlu ka-Israyeli, isililo lesi engisenzayo ngani:<verse eid="AMO 5:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="AMO 5:2"/>“Iwile iNtombi u-Israyeli,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:2">kayiphindi ivuke futhi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 5:2">ideliwe elizweni layo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:2">kungekho ongayiphakamisela phezulu.”<verse eid="AMO 5:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="AMO 5:3"/>Nanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> Wobukhosi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 5:3">“Idolobho lenu elikhupha inkulungwane eziqinileyo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:3">lizasala labalikhulu kuphela;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 5:3">idolobho elikhupha abalikhulu abaqinileyo lizasala</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:3">labalitshumi kuphela.”<verse eid="AMO 5:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="AMO 5:4"/>Nanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> endlini ka-Israyeli:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 5:4">“Dingani mina, liphile;<verse eid="AMO 5:4"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="AMO 5:5"/>lingadingi iBhetheli,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 5:5">lingayi eGiligali,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:5">lingayi eBherishebha.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 5:5">Ngoba impela iGiligali izakuya ekuthunjweni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:5">leBhetheli izadliwa iphele nya.”<verse eid="AMO 5:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="AMO 5:6"/>Dingani <char style="nd">uThixo</char> liphile</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:6">hlezi adabule phakathi kwendlu kaJosefa njengomlilo;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 5:6">uzatshisa uqothule,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:6">njalo iBhetheli kayiyikuba lomuntu ozawucitsha.<verse eid="AMO 5:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="AMO 5:7"/>Lina eliguqula ukulunga kube yibuhlungu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:7">lilahlele ubuqotho emhlabathini.<verse eid="AMO 5:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="AMO 5:8"/>Yena owenza iSilimela loMthala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:8">oguqula umnyama ube yikusa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:8">enze imini ibe yibusuku obumnyama,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 5:8">yena obiza amanzi olwandle,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:8">awathele phezu kobuso belizwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:8">
    <char style="nd">uThixo</char> yilo ibizo lakhe,<verse eid="AMO 5:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="AMO 5:9"/>wehlisela incithakalo phezu kwenqaba atshabalalise</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:9">idolobho elivikelweyo.<verse eid="AMO 5:9"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="AMO 5:10"/>Liyamzonda okhuzayo emthethwandaba limeyise</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:10">lalowo okhuluma iqiniso.<verse eid="AMO 5:10"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="AMO 5:11"/>Linyathezela umyanga limncindezele</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:11">ukuba aliphe amabele.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 5:11">Ngakho-ke, lanxa lakhe izindlu ezinkulukazi zamatshe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:11">kaliyikuhlala kuzo;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 5:11">lanxa lihlanyele izivini ezinhle,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:11">iwayini lazo kaliyikulinatha.<verse eid="AMO 5:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="AMO 5:12"/>Ngoba iziphambeko zenu ngiyazazi ukuthi zingaki</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:12">kanye lokuthi izono zenu zinkulu okunganani.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="AMO 5:12"/>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 5:12">Lincindezela abalungileyo lamukele isivalamlomo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:12">njalo emithethwandaba linqabela abayanga imfanelo.<verse eid="AMO 5:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="AMO 5:13"/>Ngakho ezikhathini ezinjalo umuntu ohlakaniphileyo uyazithulela,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:13">ngoba izikhathi zimbi.<verse eid="AMO 5:13"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="AMO 5:14"/>Dingani okuhle, hatshi okubi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:14">ukuze liphile.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 5:14">Lapho-ke <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu uSomandla uzakuba lani</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:14">njengoba lisithi ulani.<verse eid="AMO 5:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="AMO 5:15"/>Zondani okubi lithande okuhle;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:15">qinisani ukulunga emithethwandaba.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 5:15">Mhlawumbe <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu uSomandla uzakuba lomusa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:15">kuzinsalela zakoJosefa.<verse eid="AMO 5:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="AMO 5:16"/>Ngakho nanku okutshiwo yiNkosi, <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu uSomandla,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 5:16">“Kuzakuba lokulila emigwaqweni yonke</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:16">lokukhala kabuhlungu ezinkundleni zonke zikazulu.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 5:16">Abalimi bazabizwa ukuba bakhale,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:16">labakhalayo ukuba balile.<verse eid="AMO 5:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="AMO 5:17"/>Kuzakuba lokulila ezivinini zonke,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:17">ngoba ngizadlula phakathi kwenu,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:17">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.<verse eid="AMO 5:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Usuku <char style="nd">LukaThixo</char></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="AMO 5:18"/>Maye kini lina elilangazelela</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:18">usuku <char style="nd">lukaThixo</char>!</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 5:18">Kungani lilangazelela lolosuku <char style="nd">lukaThixo</char> na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:18">Lolosuku luzakuba ngumnyama, hatshi ukukhanya.<verse eid="AMO 5:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="AMO 5:19"/>Kuzafana lokuthi umuntu ubalekele isilwane</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:19">wahlangana lebhele,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 5:19">njengangathi ungene endlini yakhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:19">wabambelela emdulini ngesandla</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:19">waselunywa yinyoka.<verse eid="AMO 5:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="AMO 5:20"/>Usuku <char style="nd">lukaThixo</char> kaluyikuba ngumnyama na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:20">hatshi ukukhanya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:20">lumnyama bhuqe, kungekho nhlansi yokukhanya?<verse eid="AMO 5:20"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="AMO 5:21"/>“Ngiyayizonda, ngiyayeyisa imikhosi yokholo lwenu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:21">angingeke ngiyimele imbuthano yenu.<verse eid="AMO 5:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="AMO 5:22"/>Lanxa lingangilethela iminikelo yokutshiswa leminikelo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:22">yamabele kangiyikuyamukela.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 5:22">Lanxa liletha iminikelo emihle kakhulu yobuzalwane,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:22">lokunonisiweyo kangiyikuyinanza.<verse eid="AMO 5:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="AMO 5:23"/>Sukani lomsindo wezingoma zenu!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:23">Kangiyikuwulalela umculo wamachacho enu.<verse eid="AMO 5:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="AMO 5:24"/>Kodwa ukulunga kakugeleze njengamanzi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:24">lobuqotho njengesifula esingatshiyo!<verse eid="AMO 5:24"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="AMO 5:25"/>Kanje wake wangilethela imihlatshelo leminikelo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:25">eminyakeni engamatshumi amane enkangala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:25">wena ndlu ka-Israyeli na?<verse eid="AMO 5:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="AMO 5:26"/>Seliphakamise indawo yokukhonzela izithombe zenu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:26">isenabelo senkosi unkulunkulu wenu uSakhuthi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:26">lenkanyezi kankulunkulu wenu uKhayiwani,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:26">elazenzela khona lina ngokwenu.<verse eid="AMO 5:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="AMO 5:27"/>Ngakho ngizalisa ekuthunjweni ngale kweDamaseko,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 5:27">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> obizo lakhe nguNkulunkulu uSomandla.<verse eid="AMO 5:27"/></para>
  <chapter eid="AMO 5"/>
  <chapter number="6" style="c" sid="AMO 6"/>
  <para style="s1">Maye Kulabo Abangakhathaliyo</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="AMO 6:1"/>Maye kini lina elingakhathaliyo eZiyoni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:1">lakini elizizwa livikelekile eNtabeni iSamariya,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 6:1">lina madoda adumileyo esizwe sokuqala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:1">abantu bako-Israyeli abaya kuso!<verse eid="AMO 6:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="AMO 6:2"/>Yanini eKhaline liyikhangele;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:2">lisuka lapho yanini eHamathi enkulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:2">beselisehlela eGathi eseFilistiya.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 6:2">Bangcono kulemibuso yenu emibili na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:2">Ilizwe labo likhulu kulelenu na?<verse eid="AMO 6:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="AMO 6:3"/>Lisusa usuku olubi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:3">lisondeze eduze ukubusa ngodlakela.<verse eid="AMO 6:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="AMO 6:4"/>Lilala emibhedeni eyenziwa ngempondo zendlovu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:4">licambalale phezu kwemibheda yenu yokuphumulela.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 6:4">Lidla inyama yezimvu zekhethelo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:4">leyamathole anonisiweyo.<verse eid="AMO 6:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="AMO 6:5"/>Lihweba amachacho njengoDavida</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:5">kodwa engamachacho ezaba.<verse eid="AMO 6:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="AMO 6:6"/>Linatha iwayini ligcwele inqayi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:6">ligcobe ngamagcobo amahle,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:6">kodwa kalikhathazeki ngokuchitheka kukaJosefa.<verse eid="AMO 6:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="AMO 6:7"/>Ngakho-ke lizakuba ngabanye bakuqala ekuthunjweni;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:7">ukuzitika kwenu lokuhleka kuzaphela.<verse eid="AMO 6:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Inkosi Iyakwenyanya Ukuzigqaja Kuka-Israyeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="AMO 6:8"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> Wobukhosi uzifungele yena ngokwakhe, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu uSomandla uthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 6:8">“Ngiyakwenyanya ukuzigqaja kukaJakhobe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:8">njalo ngiyazizonda izinqaba zakhe;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 6:8">ngizalinikela idolobho lakho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:8">konke okukulo.”<verse eid="AMO 6:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="AMO 6:9"/>Nxa amadoda alitshumi esele endlini eyodwa, lawo azakufa. <verse eid="AMO 6:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="AMO 6:10"/>Njalo nxa isihlobo okumele sitshise izidumbu zifika ukuba sizisuse kuleyondlu besesibuza loba ngubani oyabe elokhu ecatshile khonapho, sithi, “Kulomunye olawe na?” Yena athi, “Hatshi,” lapho-ke uzakuthi, “Thula! Akumelanga sithinte ibizo <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>.”<verse eid="AMO 6:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="AMO 6:11"/>Ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> usekhuphe umlayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:11">njalo uzaphahlaza indlukazi ibe yizihlephu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:11">kuthi indlu encinyane ibe yizicucu.<verse eid="AMO 6:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="AMO 6:12"/>Amabhiza ayagijima emadwaleni angamawa na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:12">Umuntu uyalima khonapho ngenkabi na?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 6:12">Kodwa lina liphendule ukulunga kwaba yitshefu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:12">lesithelo sokulunga saba yibuhlungu,<verse eid="AMO 6:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="AMO 6:13"/>lina elithokoziswa yikunqotshwa kweLo-Debhari</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:13">beselisithi, “IKharinayimi kasiyithumbanga ngamandla ethu na?”<verse eid="AMO 6:13"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="AMO 6:14"/>Ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu uSomandla uthi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:14">“Ngizakuvusela isizwe, wena ndlu ka-Israyeli,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 6:14">esizakuncindezela indawo yonke</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 6:14">kusukela eLebho Hamathi kusiyafika esigodini sase-Arabha.”<verse eid="AMO 6:14"/></para>
  <chapter eid="AMO 6"/>
  <chapter number="7" style="c" sid="AMO 7"/>
  <para style="s1">Intethe, Lomlilo Lentambo Yokuqondisa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="AMO 7:1"/>Nanku engakutshengiswa <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> Wobukhosi: Wayelungisa imitshitshi yezintethe emva kokuvunwa kwesabelo senkosi khonapho amabele esibili esakhula. <verse eid="AMO 7:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="AMO 7:2"/>Kwathi lapho ilizwe seziliphundlile, ngamemeza ngathi, “<char style="nd">Thixo</char> Wobukhosi, thethelela! UJakhobe angaphepha kanjani? Mncinyane kakhulu!”<verse eid="AMO 7:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="AMO 7:3"/>Ngakho <char style="nd">uthixo</char> waxola.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="AMO 7:3">“Akusoze kwenzakale” watsho <char style="nd">uthixo</char>.<verse eid="AMO 7:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="AMO 7:4"/>Nanku engakutshengiswa <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> Wobukhosi: <char style="nd">uThixo</char> Wobukhosi wayememezela ukwehlulela ngomlilo; womisa ulwandle waqothula lelizwe. <verse eid="AMO 7:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="AMO 7:5"/>Ngakho ngamemeza ngathi “<char style="nd">Thixo</char> Wobukhosi, ngiyakuncenga, ake ume! UJakhobe angaphepha kanjani na? Mncinyane kakhulu!”<verse eid="AMO 7:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="AMO 7:6"/>Ngakho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> waxola.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="AMO 7:6">“Lokhu lakho akuyikwenzakala,” kwatsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> Wobukhosi.<verse eid="AMO 7:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="AMO 7:7"/>Nanku angitshengisa khona: uThixo wayemi phansi komduli owawakhiwe waqonda nta ephethe intambo yokuqondisa ngesandla sakhe <verse eid="AMO 7:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="AMO 7:8"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasengibuza esithi, “Kuyini okubonayo, Amosi?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="AMO 7:8">Ngaphendula ngathi, “Yintambo yokuqondisa.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="AMO 7:8">UThixo wasesithi, “Khangela, ngibeka intambo yokuqondisa phakathi kwabantu bami bako-Israyeli; kangisayikubaxolela futhi.<verse eid="AMO 7:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="AMO 7:9"/>Izindawo eziphakemeyo zika-Isaka zizadilizwa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 7:9">lezindawo ezingcwele zako-Israyeli zizachithwa;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 7:9">indlu kaJerobhowamu ngizayihlasela ngenkemba yami.”<verse eid="AMO 7:9"/></para>
  <para style="s1">U-Amosi Lo-Amaziya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="AMO 7:10"/>U-Amaziya umphristi waseBhetheli wathumela ilizwi kuJerobhowamu inkosi yako-Israyeli, wathi, “U-Amosi uceba okubi ngawe khona kanye phakathi kwako-Israyeli. Ilizwe lingeke limelane lawo wonke amazwi akhe. <verse eid="AMO 7:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="AMO 7:11"/>Ngoba u-Amosi uthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 7:11">‘UJerobhowamu uzakufa ngenkemba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 7:11">njalo impela u-Israyeli uzathunjwa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 7:11">asiwe khatshana kwelizwe lakibo.’ ”<verse eid="AMO 7:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="AMO 7:12"/>U-Amaziya wasesithi ku-Amosi, “Phuma, wena mboni! Buyela elizweni lakoJuda, usebenzele ukudla kwakho khonale wenze lokuphrofetha kwakho khonale. <verse eid="AMO 7:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="AMO 7:13"/>Ungaphrofithi futhi eBhetheli, ngoba le yindawo yenkosi kanye lethempeli lombuso.”<verse eid="AMO 7:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="AMO 7:14"/>U-Amosi waphendula u-Amaziya wathi, “Mina ngangingasuye mphrofethi kumbe indodana yomphrofethi, kodwa ngangingumelusi, njalo ngigcina izihlahla zomkhiwa wesikhamore. <verse eid="AMO 7:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="AMO 7:15"/>Kodwa <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wangithatha ekweluseni imihlambi yezimvu wathi kimi, ‘Hamba uyephrofetha ebantwini bami bako-Israyeli.’ <verse eid="AMO 7:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="AMO 7:16"/>Ngakho-ke khathesi zwana ilizwi <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>. Wena uthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 7:16">‘Ungaphrofethi kubi ngo-Israyeli,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 7:16">njalo yekela ukutshumayela kubi ngendlela ka-Isaka.’<verse eid="AMO 7:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="AMO 7:17"/>Ngakho-ke nanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 7:17">‘Umkakho uzakuba yisifebe edolobheni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 7:17">amadoda lamadodakazi akho azakufa ngenkemba.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 7:17">Ilizwe lakho lizalinganiswa labiwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 7:17">njalo wena ngokwakho uzafela elizweni lamaqaba.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 7:17">Njalo impela u-Israyeli uzathunjwa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 7:17">asiwe khatshana kwelizwe lakhe.’ ”<verse eid="AMO 7:17"/></para>
  <chapter eid="AMO 7"/>
  <chapter number="8" style="c" sid="AMO 8"/>
  <para style="s1">Isitsha Sezithelo Ezivuthiweyo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="AMO 8:1"/>Nanku engakutshengiswa <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> Wobukhosi: isitsha esilezithelo ezivuthiweyo. <verse eid="AMO 8:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="AMO 8:2"/>Wangibuza wathi, “Kuyini okubonayo, Amosi?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="AMO 8:2">Mina ngaphendula ngathi, “Yisitsha esilezithelo ezivuthiweyo.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="AMO 8:2">
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kimi, “Isikhathi sabantu bami bako-Israyeli sesifikile; kangisabaxoleli futhi.<verse eid="AMO 8:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="AMO 8:3"/>Ngalolosuku, izingoma zethempelini zizaphenduka zibe yikulila. Izidumbu ezinengi kakhulu zidaklazelwe indawo yonke! Thulani!” Kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> Wobukhosi.<verse eid="AMO 8:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="AMO 8:4"/>Zwanini lokhu, lina elincindezela abaswelayo njalo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:4">lichitha labayanga elizweni,<verse eid="AMO 8:4"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="AMO 8:5"/>lisithi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 8:5">“Ukuthwasa kweNyanga Entsha kuzaphela nini</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:5">ukuze sithengise amabele,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 8:5">leSabatha lidlule</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:5">ukuze sithengise ingqoloyi na?”</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 8:5">Sinciphise isilinganiso,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:5">sikhweze intengo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:5">siqilibezele ngezilinganiso zenkohliso,<verse eid="AMO 8:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="AMO 8:6"/>sithenge abayanga ngesiliva,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:6">abaswelayo sibathenge ngamanyathelo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:6">sithengise lamakhoba ngengqoloyi.<verse eid="AMO 8:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="AMO 8:7"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> ufungile ngokuziQhenya kukaJakhobe wathi, “Angisoze ngakhohliswa loba yini abayenzileyo.<verse eid="AMO 8:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="AMO 8:8"/>Ilizwe kaliyikuthuthumela ngalokhu yini</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:8">labo bonke abahlala kulo kabayikulila na?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 8:8">Ilizwe lonke lizaqubuka njengeNayili;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:8">lizadungeka beselitshona phansi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:8">njengomfula waseGibhithe.<verse eid="AMO 8:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="AMO 8:9"/>Ngalolosuku,” kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> Wobukhosi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 8:9">“ngizakwenza ilanga litshone emini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:9">ngenze emhlabeni kube mnyama emini ekhanyayo.<verse eid="AMO 8:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="AMO 8:10"/>Ngizaphendula imikhosi yenu yokukhonza ibe yikulila</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:10">lokuhlabelela kwenu konke kube yikukhala.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 8:10">Lonke ngizalenza ligqoke amasaka,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:10">njalo liphuce amakhanda enu.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 8:10">Lesosikhathi ngizasenza sifane lokulilela indodana eyiyo yodwa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:10">lokuphela kwaso kube njengosuku olubuhlungu.<verse eid="AMO 8:10"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="AMO 8:11"/>Insuku ziyeza, kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> Wobukhosi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:11">lapho engizathumela khona indlala elizweni</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 8:11">hatshi indlala yokudla kumbe ukomela amanzi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:11">kodwa indlala yokuzwa amazwi <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>.<verse eid="AMO 8:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="AMO 8:12"/>Abantu bazaphamazela besuka elwandle besiya elwandle,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:12">njalo bazule kusukela enyakatho kusiya empumalanga,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 8:12">bedinga ilizwi <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:12">kodwa kabayikulithola.<verse eid="AMO 8:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="AMO 8:13"/>Ngalolosuku</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 8:13">izintombi ezinhle lezinsizwa eziqinileyo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:13">zizaqaleka ngenxa yokoma.<verse eid="AMO 8:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="AMO 8:14"/>Bona labo abafunga ngesono seSamariya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:14">loba bathi, ‘Ngeqiniso</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:14">njengoba unkulunkulu wakho ephila, wena Dani,’</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 8:14">loba bathi, ‘Ngeqiniso</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:14">njengoba unkulunkulu waseBherishebha ephila,’</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 8:14">bazakuwa, bangaphindi bavuke futhi.”<verse eid="AMO 8:14"/></para>
  <chapter eid="AMO 8"/>
  <chapter number="9" style="c" sid="AMO 9"/>
  <para style="s1">U-Israyeli Uzachithwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="AMO 9:1"/>Ngabona uThixo emi phansi kwe-alithari, wasesithi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 9:1">“Tshaya izihloko zensika</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:1">ukuze imibundu inyikinyeke.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 9:1">Ziwisele phansi phezu kwamakhanda abantu bonke;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:1">labo abazasala ngizababulala ngenkemba.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 9:1">Kakho lamunye ozaphunyuka,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:1">kakho ozabaleka.<verse eid="AMO 9:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="AMO 9:2"/>Loba besimba baze bafike ekudepheni kwengcwaba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:2">isandla sami sizabathatha khonapho.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 9:2">Loba bekhwela baye phezulu emazulwini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:2">bekhonapho ngizabehlisela phansi.<verse eid="AMO 9:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="AMO 9:3"/>Loba becatsha engqongweni yeKhameli,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:3">khonapho ngizabadinga ngibabambe.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 9:3">Loba bengicatshela enzikini yolwandle,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:3">khonapho ngizalaya inyoka ukuba ibalume.<verse eid="AMO 9:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="AMO 9:4"/>Loba izitha zabo zingabasa ekuthunjweni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:4">khonale ngizalaya inkemba ukuba ibabulale.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="AMO 9:4"/>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 9:4">Ngizagxilisa amehlo ami kubo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:4">ngenxa yobubi hatshi ngobuhle.”<verse eid="AMO 9:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="AMO 9:5"/>INkosi, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uSomandla,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 9:5">yena othinta umhlaba uncibilike,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:5">kuthi bonke abahlezi kuwo bakhale,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 9:5">ilizwe lonke liyaphakama njengoNayili</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:5">liphinde litshone phansi njengomfula waseGibhithe,<verse eid="AMO 9:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="AMO 9:6"/>yena owakha indlu yakhe yobukhosi ephakemeyo emazulwini</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:6">njalo ubeka isisekelo sakhe phezu komhlaba,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 9:6">ebiza amanzi olwandle</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:6">awathele phezu kobuso bomhlaba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:6">
    <char style="nd">uThixo</char> yilo ibizo lakhe.<verse eid="AMO 9:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="AMO 9:7"/>“Lina ma-Israyeli,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:7">kimi kalinjengamaKhushi na?”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:7">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 9:7">“U-Israyeli kangimkhuphanga eGibhithe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:7">lamaFilistiya eKhafithori,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:7">kanye lama-Aramu eKhiri na?<verse eid="AMO 9:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="AMO 9:8"/>Impela amehlo <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> Wobukhosi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:8">aphezu kombuso olesono.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 9:8">Ngizawukhucula ebusweni bomhlaba</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:8">ikanti indlu kaJakhobe</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 9:8">angiyikuyichitha ngokupheleleyo,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:8">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.<verse eid="AMO 9:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="AMO 9:9"/>“Ngoba ngizakupha umlayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:9">njalo ngizahlungula indlu ka-Israyeli</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:9">phakathi kwezizwe zonke</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 9:9">njengokuhlungulwa kwamabele ekhomaneni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:9">njalo akukho hlamvu oluzawela phansi.<verse eid="AMO 9:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="AMO 9:10"/>Izoni zonke phakathi kwabantu bami</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:10">zizakufa ngenkemba,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 9:10">bonke labo abathi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:10">‘Umonakalo kawuyikusifica loba usihlangabeze.’ ”<verse eid="AMO 9:10"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubuyiswa Kuka-Israyeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="AMO 9:11"/>“Ngalolosuku</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 9:11">ngizavusa ithente likaDavida elawayo.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:11">Ngizavala izikhala zalo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:11">ngivuselele okwadilikayo kwalo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:11">ngilakhe njengelaliyikho khona,<verse eid="AMO 9:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="AMO 9:12"/>ukuze bathathe insalela ye-Edomi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:12">kanye lezizwe zonke ezizabizwa ngebizo lami,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:12">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, ozazenza lezizinto.<verse eid="AMO 9:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="AMO 9:13"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> uthi, “Zinsuku ziyeza,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 9:13">lapho ovunayo ezaficwa ngolimayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:13">lohlanyelayo aficwe ngokhama amavini.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 9:13">Iwayini elitsha lizagobhoza ezintabeni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:13">njalo ligeleze emaqaqeni wonke.<verse eid="AMO 9:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="AMO 9:14"/>Ngizababuyisela abantu bami</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:14">bako-Israyeli abathunjwayo.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="AMO 9:14"/>
  <para style="q1" vid="AMO 9:14">Bazawakha kutsha amadolobho adilikayo bahlale kuwo.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:14">Bazahlanyela izivini banathe iwayini lazo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:14">bazakwenza izivande badle izithelo zazo.<verse eid="AMO 9:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="AMO 9:15"/>Ngizagxumeka u-Israyeli elizweni lakhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:15">angaphindi asitshunwe futhi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="AMO 9:15">elizweni engimnike lona,”</para>
  <para style="m" vid="AMO 9:15">kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu.<verse eid="AMO 9:15"/></para>
  <chapter eid="AMO 9"/>
</usx>
